data.description: This and is the house you have been waiting for it sets on 4 acres (owner). A live in basement that has two bedrooms and full bath with its own private laundry room. A large kitchen with A room off the kitchen that could be used for A pantry. A living room facing the back side of the property and two rooms that could be used for extra bedrooms or private office. The main level has three bedrooms with the master on the main and three baths with A country kitchen with lots of cabinets and storage space. There is A bay window overlooking the back of the property. A wood burning fireplace in the living room. There is a mud room off the kitchen from the back deck.  A nice private country setting with lots of nature to be enjoyed. The house comes with solar panels that supplies power for the house. There is A Garage /workshop and a greenhouse for all your hobby and gardening experiences.
